episodes.title: Ex Cult Member of Yellow Deli exposes Sinister Cult! (Full interview)
episodes.description:
(Disclaimer) This Video is for educational, Documentary Purposes. We do NOT support the Yellow Deli or Twelve Tribes Cult. We are educating people about what this place is really like and hopefully we can save victims and prevent future ones. 
Ben and I went undercover inside this Cult called the Twelve Tribes aka the Yellow deli and exposed them for their messed up beliefs and a guy we secretly recorded inside the cult is now out of the cult and we ended up interviewing him and having him answer unanswered questions from our series.
